# Future Interns - Data Science Task 1

## Business Sales Performance Dashboard

This project analyzes business sales data using a dashboard created from the Superstore dataset.

### Objectives
- Analyze sales performance by category
- Compare sales across regions
- Identify top-selling products
- Observe monthly sales trends

### Tools Used
- Google Sheets / Excel
- CSV Dataset

### Key Insights
- Technology category generated the highest sales.
- West region showed strong performance.
- Top-selling products contributed major revenue.
- Monthly sales trends revealed peak demand periods.

### Files Included
- Superstore.csv
- Dashboard PDF
- README.md
